          3(20-CA-40(N,EL),,WID,,G)
          4(20-CA-40(N,G),,WID)
ANALYSIS  1A standard Bayes' theorem analysis was used to assign
           the resonances to either p or d wave sequence, below
           130 keV.
ASSUMED    (ASSUM1,20-CA-40(N,EL),,WID) Assumed for analysis.
           (ASSUM2,20-CA-40(N,EL),,WID,,G) The values are cited
            from Singh et al.,Phys.Rev.C10(1974)2143, and
            Johnson,priv.comm.thru ORNL-DWG73-4301,4302,8791,8792.
FLAG      1(1.) Momentum assignment from gamma-ray spectra.
           (2.) Assignment from large high energy component of
            spectrum.
ERR-ANALYS (DATA-ERR) No information on the source of uncertainty
